3- 修改 angular.json 定义组件和的前缀

   (1) tslint.json 
        "directive-selector": [true, "attribute", "zy", "camelCase"],
        "component-selector": [true, "element", "zy", "kebab-case"],
   (2) angularn.json
       "schematics": {
        "@schematics/angular:component": {
            "prefix": "zy",
            "styleExt": "scss"
        },
        "@schematics/angular:directive": {
            "spec": false,
            "prefix": "zy"
        },
        
